About:
------

MLAPD is a Mailing List manager which uses LDAP to control lists access. It's written in Python and designed to work with Postfix as an Access Policy Delegation daemon.


Requirments:
------------

* Python ( >= 2.4 )

Postfix and LDAP are not needed on the server machine where you are going to install MLAPD, but they are needed to made MLAPD working :+)


Reporting bugs:
---------------

You can see open issues and submit new bug at: http://code.google.com/p/mlapd/issues/list